        <section id="methodology">
            <h1>Methodology</h1>
            <p>The project is structured in different work packages that cover the analysis of cognitive, ethical, and deliberative capabilities of language models.</p>
            <h2>Work Packages</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>WP1:</strong> Evaluation of LLMs' cognitive capabilities.</li>
                <li><strong>WP2:</strong> Investigation of the applicability of LLMs in bioethics.</li>
                <li><strong>WP3:</strong> Use of LLMs to support democratic deliberation.</li>
            </ul>
